---
import Layout from '@/components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Start a Club" description="Step-by-step guide to starting a ruck club">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Start a Club</h1>
  <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
      <p>Starting a ruck club is a rewarding way to build community, improve fitness, and share the benefits of rucking with others. This guide provides practical steps to launch your own successful ruck club.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Leadership Principles</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
        <li>Vision: Clearly define what you want to achieve with your club.</li>
        <li>Planning: Develop a structured approach to launching and growing.</li>
        <li>Communication: Keep members informed and engaged.</li>
        <li>Adaptability: Be ready to adjust based on feedback and circumstances.</li>
        <li>Service: Focus on providing value to your members.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Practical Checklist</h2>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
        <li>Research local interest and potential meeting locations.</li>
        <li>Define your club's purpose, values, and target audience.</li>
        <li>Set up a simple communication system (social media group, email list).</li>
        <li>Plan your first ruck event with a beginner-friendly route.</li>
        <li>Establish basic safety guidelines and equipment recommendations.</li>
        <li>Promote your launch through local networks and social media.</li>
        <li>Host your first ruck and gather feedback for improvement.</li>
        <li>Establish a regular meeting schedule based on member availability.</li>
        <li>Continuously evaluate and improve the club experience.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Downloadable Checklist</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="/checklists/start-a-club.pdf" class="btn btn-primary" download>
          Download Printable Checklist (PDF)
        </a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
